---
/* Medical disclaimer block — fixed content, no props */
---

<aside class="medical-disclaimer" aria-label="醫療聲明">
  <div class="medical-disclaimer__header">
    <svg
      class="medical-disclaimer__icon"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="20"
      height="20"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
    </svg>
    <strong class="medical-disclaimer__title">醫療聲明</strong>
  </div>
  <p class="medical-disclaimer__text">
    本站所有內容僅供一般健康資訊參考，不構成醫療診斷、治療建議或處方。如有任何健康問題，請諮詢合格的醫療專業人員。
  </p>
  <a class="medical-disclaimer__link" href="/medical-disclaimer/">完整醫療聲明</a>
</aside>

<style>
  .medical-disclaimer {
    background-color: var(--color-paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-fog);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .medical-disclaimer__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .medical-disclaimer__icon {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .medical-disclaimer__title {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .medical-disclaimer__text {
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--color-ink) 65%, transparent);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .medical-disclaimer__link {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--color-teal);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.15em;
  }

  .medical-disclaimer__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-teal-hover);
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
  }
</style>
